episodes.title: Slain couple's daughter arrested along with leader of cultlike group
episodes.description:
A Pennsylvania woman who was a person of interest in her parents' murders in 2022 was arrested in Maryland, along with the apparent leader of a cultlike group connected to homicides across three states.
